additionalProperty.name: Warning
additionalProperty.value: Always read the label and follow directions for use. For advice contact the Poisons Information Centre (Phone: Australia 13 11 26) or a doctor. If swallowed, do Not induce vomiting. Give a glass of water to drink. If skin contact occurs, wash skin thoroughly. If in eyes, wash out with a large amount of water. If irritation persists, contact a doctor. Contains no phosphates.
